'''Jorge Rabassa''' is an [[Argentine people|Argentine]] [[geomorphologist]] and [[Quaternary geology|Quaternary geologist]]. He is a professor at [[National University of Tierra del Fuego]] and director of the [[National Scientific and Technical Research Council|CONICET]].<ref>[http://www.isgs.illinois.edu/node/8855 Argentinian Quaternary Geologist Jorge Rabassa to Return to ISGS in 2015]</ref><ref>[http://www.radiofueguina.com/2016/04/el-dr-jorge-rabassa-distinguido-por-universidad-de-estados-unidos/ El Dr. Jorge Rabassa, distinguido por Universidad de Estados Unidos]</ref> He is member of the [[National Academy of Sciences of Argentina]] since 2012.<ref name=aaaa>[http://www.8300.com.ar/2012/11/29/el-geologo-jorge-rabassa-ingresara-manana-a-la-academia-de-ciencias/ El geólogo Jorge Rabassa ingresará mañana a la Academia Nacional de Ciencias]</ref> From 1998 to 2002 he served as rector of the [[National University of Comahue]].<ref name=aaaa/>  

